## Design Specifications

### Layout Dimensions
- **Width:** 400px (mobile/tablet), 500px (desktop lg:)
- **Height:** Full viewport (`h-screen`)
- **Position:** Fixed top-right (`fixed top-0 right-0`)
- **Slide animation:** `transition-transform duration-200 ease-in-out`

### Color Palette

**Dark Mode (Terminal Aesthetic):**
- Background: `bg-black` (#000000)
- User text: `text-white` (#FFFFFF)
- AI text: `text-green-400` (#4ADE80 - terminal green)
- Border: `border-border-dark`

**Light Mode (Modern Terminal):**
- Background: `bg-white` (#FFFFFF)
- User text: `text-text-light-primary` (black)
- AI text: `text-orange-600` (#EA580C - warm orange)
- Border: `border-border-light`

### Typography
- **Font:** `font-mono` (monospace)
- **Sizes:**
  - Header: `text-sm`
  - Messages: `text-sm`
  - Input: `text-sm`
  - Metadata: `text-xs`

### Spacing
- **Padding:** Header `px-4 py-3`, Messages `px-4 py-2`
- **Gap:** Between elements `gap-2` or `gap-3`

